# @helix/bundle

Syntactically validates bundle structure and signatures.

## Installation

Install using [npm](https://www.npmjs.org/):
```
npm install @helix/bundle
```

or using [yarn](https://yarnpkg.com/):

```
yarn add @helix/bundle
```

